Interface IData

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Data, DataOfString

    public interface IData
    Payload - Sensors are producing data at quite a big rate. We can leave the cleanup up to Java itself (garbage collection with DataOfString) or we can try to manage it ourself with the Data class.
